org.tron.trident.core

Class ApiWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tron.trident.core.ApiWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Api

    public class ApiWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Api
    A ApiWrapper object is the entry point for calling the functions.

    A ApiWrapper object is bind with a private key and a full node. broadcastTransaction(org.tron.trident.proto.Chain.Transaction), signTransaction(org.tron.trident.proto.Response.TransactionExtention, org.tron.trident.core.key.KeyPair) and other transaction related operations can be done via a ApiWrapper object.

    Since:
    java version 1.8.0_231
    See Also:
    Contract, Chain.Transaction, Contract
